data.description:
Calling on all the buyers who would like to be in a well established neighborhood, close to Ft. Liberty and Triangle!!! The house is PRICED to SELL!!! Don't wait to schedule a showing and send an offer. Check the comps, it will not last long. 2-story home offers spacious living room with fireplace, formal dining room with hardwood floors and open eat-in kitchen. All bedrooms are located on the second floor, with the master bedroom being on the opposite side of the house. Master bedroom offers 2 walk-in closets and master bath with dual vanities, garden tub and separate shower. There are other 2 bedrooms and a full bath on the top floor, as well as another enormous size room that can be used as a 4th bedroom, and has a separate office space.
Kitchen and all bathrooms have updated flooring. All this house may need is a fresh coat of paint and new carpets.
The property is sold AS IS. Sellers will consider Appraisal contingent repairs.
